values:
Wow, been blown off twice today..

What the hell am I going to do when you go to school?

I'm debating two pretty serious things in my head right now, one I've been dreaming about every time my eyes shut and I fall asleep, and one that I can't escape from even when I go on vacation..AHHh..but both are driving my mind crazy. I kind of wish you could talk to people about things, discuss it, but then have them not remember after the conversation is ended..

Stay with me, don't go.  That's what you have ALL school year without me for. GRRR! SO anyways, never ever writing checks again. jerk faces at sports authority....
SO ANGRY!!

How to make a Alyssa
Ingredients:
5 parts competetiveness
1 part silliness
5 parts
Method:
Blend at a low speed for 30 seconds. Top it off with a sprinkle of emotion and enjoy!
